query:
SELECT 
                s.id,
                s.name,
                s.description,
                s.folder_id, 
                s.created_at as "created_at!: chrono::DateTime<chrono::Utc>",
                CAST(COUNT(p.id) AS INTEGER) as project_count
            FROM 
                series s
            LEFT JOIN 
                projects p ON s.id = p.series_id
            GROUP BY 
                s.id, s.name, s.description, s.folder_id, s.created_at
            ORDER BY 
                s.name
